title: Chance Machine 5
overview:
Chance Machine 5
    
        Play Chance Machine 5 demo slot online for fun. Enjoy free casino games in demo mode on Casino Guru. Expert review included.
about_game: This high volatility, and reasonable RTP (96.0%) slot has a vintage mood.

Theme and Storyline.text:
With a classic aesthetic, this slot is part of the Chance Machine series.
Everything about this game says good, old-fashioned casino. This is an ideal slot for players looking for a nostalgic experience.
Set against a dark burgundy background, the reels are framed in shiny gold. The symbols portray the four card suits, but in jewel form. These are eye-catching and make it easy to spot win lines.
For those longing for the casinos of days gone by, this game will be a lot of fun. It has the festive spirit that suggests smoky air and clinking glasses.
Players could be forgiven for grabbing a tux or red mini dress to really get into it.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
The animation has a somewhat vintage feel. The card suit symbols are not particularly original, but that’s not the point of this game. It has a style for players in the mood for something familiar.
The rich jewel tones of the spades, diamonds, clubs, and hearts are jovial. They maintain the party atmosphere that this slot is all about. The illustration of the gems is minimal, but suggests depth and sparkle.
With no background music, this game keeps things simple with a satisfying flicking sound as the reels spin. The occasional dings bring to mind a cash register, and keep money on the players mind.
Overall, players will feel they’ve found a little of the grit and glamour of a ‘70s casino.

media.caption: Win in the Chance Machine 5 slot machine

Gameplay.text:
Chance Machine 5 is a five reel, three row slot, with five win lines.
Things get interesting with the gamble option. Players choose a card from a selection of four. If they beat the Dealer’s pick, their win doubles. Players then get to gamble again. However, if the Dealer wins at any point, players lose their winnings and the game ends.
Gameplay is straightforward and quick. Players will enjoy spins easily leading from one to the next.

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Scatter symbols.
The Wild symbol expands vertically to complete combinations, and only appears on reels 2, 3, and 4. This adds some interesting variation.
This game has two Scatter symbols, the Yellow Scatter appearing on all reels, and the White Scatter appears on reels 1, 3, and 5 only.

Bet Sizes, RTP and Variance.text:
The return to player of this game is 96.0%, which is bang on our yardstick for average of roughly 96%.
The range of bets on the site we tested ran from a minimum bet per spin of $/£/€0.05 up to a maximum of $/£/€50.00 per spin.
The volatility of this game is high, which makes it a good match for our preferred slot machine strategies. Our slot strategies target the highest possible volatility.

media.caption: Full paytable for Chance Machine 5 slot machine

Conclusion.text:
Due to the decent RTP and high volatility, we recommend this game.
The nostalgic graphics make this slot an especially good fit for players looking for a classic slot experience.
The mostly standard gameplay is ideal for players who are looking to relax with something familiar.

A retro chilled-out soundtrack ensures that players will feel they’ve stepped onto the Las Vegas strip in a past decade. The reels spin with a rustic clicking sound, adding to the feeling that this is a physical slot machine complete with vintage machinery.

Gameplay.text:
Super Joker Megaways uses a simplified version of the Megaways system, randomizing the number of symbols that appear in each reel for each spin. This can vary from 2 to 8 symbols per reel. Unlike the usual Megaways format which sports six reels, this slot only had three. As a result the number of maximum winways tops out at 512, rather than the usual 117,000.
Wins are awarded for landing matching symbols in adjacent reels, starting from the leftmost reel and going towards the rightmost.
The Cascade feature means that winning combinations vanish, allowing new symbols to fall from above to take their place. Scatter symbols do not take part in the Cascades.

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:

The Gamble feature means that players can decide to bet their winnings in a game of double-or-nothing. Players place their bet on either red or black and draw a card from an infinite deck. If they win, they double their bet and may continue. If they lose, the feature concludes and their winnings are lost.

Gameplay.text:
Elemento is a nine reel, nine row slot.
The play area of this game is a 7x7 grid, while the top and bottom rows and left and right reels are the Element area. This area is only filled by Element Wild symbols and empty positions. Symbols in the Element area do not fall away during Cascades.
Wins are awarded for clusters of 5 or more matching symbols landing horizontally or vertically.
The Cascade feature means that regular symbols and Wild symbols that make up any cluster wins fall away, so that new symbols may fall into their positions. Cascades continue until no more there are no more Cluster wins.

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild symbol substitutes for all regular symbols. Wild symbols may be placed on the reels by the Fire Wild symbol.
This game also has four Element Wild symbols that appear in the Element area of the reels. After players spin, 4 random Element Wilds will land in random positions, and each can act as a Wild symbol.
During the Cascade feature, the Element area rotates clockwise one position for every Cascade.
When an Element Wild becomes part of Cluster win, they become activated, which increases an Element meter by 1. These activated symbols can no longer be part of Cluster wins.
After no more Cluster wins or Cascades are possible, activated Wild symbols activate their corresponding special feature.
When a cluster win does not contain an Element Wild, there is a chance of spawning a randomly placed Element Wild.
When players activate one of each of the Element Wild symbols, the Free Spins feature will begin. Players will start with 5 free spins and one for each of the Element Wilds they have activated.
During the Free Spins feature, there is a multiplier. The multiplier starts at 1 and increases by 1 every time the player triggers a cascade.
Players can buy directly into the Free Spin feature.

title: Run Amuck
overview:
Run Amuck
    
        Play Run Amuck demo slot online for fun. Enjoy free casino games in demo mode on Casino Guru. Expert review included.
about_game: This average RTP (96%), high volatility science lab-themed slot is an experiment gone right.

Theme and Storyline.text:
This slot is themed around a mad scientist’s lab.
Immediately, players will discover petri dishes filled with adorable goopy creatures. The colourful little characters have been brought to life by strange experiments.
Players will have to pour mysterious substances together and cross their fingers that they get the combinations right. They may just create a whole host of slime friends as they play.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
The background music is a cheerful series of sci-fi chimes and beeps. This creates a quirky atmosphere and sets the mood to do daring chemistry experiments.
Hitting 'spin' prompts a satisfying sliding sound that makes it feel as though players are combining odd ingredients.
Players have the option to mute only the music or only the gameplay sound effects so they can curate the experience they most enjoy.
The stars of this game are the endearingly cute goo creatures. Made of glimmering slime in bright shades of blue, orange, green and fuchsia pink, they look out from the reels with friendly expressions. Players will be keen to spin just to see what irresistible creature appears next.
The setting of the game is a whimsical cartoon lab, complete flasks of bubbling liquid and gleaming pipes. Players will have no doubt they have entered the workspace of an eccentric scientist.
Overall, the animation and soundtrack create a great atmosphere that’s fun to visit.

media.caption: Win in the Run Amuck slot machine

Gameplay.text:
Run Amuck is a seven reel, seven row slot.
Wins are awarded for landing clusters of 4 or more matching symbols (connected either vertically or horizontally).
Upon wins, the clusters collapse together to combine into symbols that take up as few positions as possible.
After this combining, the other symbols on the reels vanish and new symbols appear to take their place. The process repeats until no new combinations can be formed.
The pace of the gameplay is lively and captivating. Players will have no trouble staying engaged with this one.

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
There is no Wild symbol, but there is a Bonus symbol which initiates Free Spins.
The Free Spins feature is triggered when the Bonus symbol lands 3 times (awarded 8 free games), or 4 times (awarding 30 free games).
The Bonus symbol will only land on the bottom left, bottom right, top left, and top right positions.
While in the Free Spins feature, a special set of reels are used, and players begin with a select number of watching symbols on the reels.
Free Spins rounds play at the same bet as the game was initiated on.

media.caption: Big win in the Run Amuck slot

Bet Sizes, RTP and Variance.text:
The return to player of this game is 96%, which is exactly at our yardstick for average RTP.
The range of bets on the site we tested ran from a minimum bet per spin of $/£/€0.20 up to a maximum of $/£/€400 per spin.
The volatility of this game is high, which makes it a good match for our preferred slot machine strategies. Our slot strategies target the highest possible volatility.

media.caption: Full paytable for Run Amuck slot machine

Conclusion.text:
We recommend this average RTP, high volatility science experiment-themed slot.
The playful theme and cute characters make this game a lot of fun visually while the high volatility is great for players following our slot strategies.
The bonuses and eye-catching gameplay add an extra bit of allure to this engaging game.

Theme and Story Line.text:
Star Clusters MegaClusters is a simple gem-themed slot. The reels exist in a blank yellow universe, while the reels are made up of simple, geometric crystals.
The gameplay format is front and centre with the theme being a simple adornment.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
The design elements of Star Clusters MegaClusters are all pretty simple. The symbols are gems, the background is a yellow gradient. The reels have a few bells and whistles but they all keep things simple.
However, the mechanics of the game (details below) lend themselves to extensive animations. The various meters all flash blue and white, this slot's equivalent to a cascade feature involves other eruptions of light. The simple backgrounds change and move as the game develops. Everything is kept in motion to keep the slot visually engaging despite the simplicity of the design elements.
All this is accompanied by music and sound effects that match perfectly the candy-crush-like visuals.

media.caption: Big win in the Star Clusters MegaClusters slot

Gameplay.text:
Star Clusters MegaClusters is played on a four-by-four grid of symbols. Winning combinations are made up of any group of five or more matching symbols that are in contact vertically or horizontally.
The MegaClusters system removes any winning symbols and replaces them with four smaller symbols. If a winning combo results that involves these smaller symbols, those symbols are re-spun after being removed. Each time this happens, it is called a Reaction.
This process repeats until no new winning symbols occur.

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild symbols substitute for all other symbols. There are two kinds of Wild symbols: Wilds and Gold Wilds.
Gold Wilds function like regular Wilds. However, they have a multiplier attached. The multiplier starts at one, but with each win that includes a Gold Wild, the multiplier increases by one. At the end of a spin, the multiplier resets to one.
If a player has five or more reactions in one spin, they trigger the Free Spin bonus. The player gets two free spins, plus an additional free spin for every reaction over five in the triggering spin.
Players can earn two additional free spins for every ten Gold Wilds they hit. The Gold Wild multiplier does not reset during Free Spins.

media.caption: Multiplier increases by one when win includes a Gold Wild, and resets at the end of the spin

The volatility of this game is high, which makes it a good match for our preferred slot machine strategies. Our slot strategies target the highest possible volatility.

media.caption: Full paytable of the Star Clusters MegaClusters slot machine

Conclusion.text:
Star Clusters MegaClusters is an excellent slot.
The MegaClusters system is a recent but welcome addition to the realm of slot mechanics. This version of it is a pretty bare bones set up from a thematic point of view, but the combination of good gameplay, high volatility and a decent RTP leave us pretty enamoured with this slot overall.
It gets our recommendation.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:

Players will feel as if they are weightlessly hovering over the brightly-hued cube reels. The dark backdrop adds to this feeling with ghostly shapes of other blocks floating in the distance.

Gameplay.text:
Cubes 2 is a five reel, five row slot.
Wins are awarded for landing 5 or more matching symbols in adjacent reels.
If a player lands a winning combination, then the reels expand, growing to a 7x7 grid. If a new winning combination is landed, or if the existing winning combination grows, then the reels expand once more to become a 11x11 grid.
Wins are only awarded after the reels stop expanding.

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Corner Multipliers appear with an X on them at each corner of the initial reel grid. If one of the Corner Multipliers forms part of a winning combination, then the X is replaced by a number decided by the number of symbols in the winning combination. That number is applied as a multiplier to the final win.
When winning combinations are connected to multiple Corner Multipliers, the final win is multiplied by the value of both multipliers added together.
Players can trigger the Free Spins feature by landing 5 or more winning combinations in different colors.
The Free Spins feature begins with 5 free spins, and players begin the feature by selecting a Mystery Cube to determine a cube color that will be sticky throughout the feature.

overview:

about_game: This high RTP (96.71%), high volatility East Asian kite-themed slot will take players soaring.

Theme and Storyline.text:
This slot is themed around East Asian kites.
Players hover in a sunset sky among a flock of whimsical kites including birds, fish, and of course a fierce dragon. The dragon most of all seems to be a living creature among paper kites.
The festival atmosphere is captivating, as players test their will to see who will fly the highest. The dreamy nature of this world is uplifting and easy to get lost in.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
The soundtrack is a gentle series of flute-like melodies. This reinforces the sense that players are in a fantasy East Asian setting.
The animation of the sunset backdrop is breathtaking and calming. The gradient of blue, purple, and orange bring to mind a watercolour painting. A blur of white birds occasionally glides by, suggesting players are at least as high as a bird might fly.
The symbols suggest various types of kites from a rainbow butterfly, to a ship with sails full of wind, to brighty hued fish in traditional designs. It’s easy to imagine the colourful creatures soaring high above the ground, suspended by wind.
A beautiful girl peers out from one symbol, her hair combed into an intricate hair piece. She looks at the player with an alluring gaze.
The dragon symbol explodes from his reel with horns and whiskers extending beyond its limits. His expression is crazed and furious as if he is heading into battle.
Overall, the front end of this game has a delightful aesthetic that is both engrossing and calming.

media.alt: Floating Dragon Hold & Spin big win
media.caption: Big win in the Floating Dragon Hold and Spin slot machine

Gameplay.text:
Floating Dragon Hold and Spin is a five reel, three row slot, with 10 win lines.
The gameplay stays fast and engaging. Players will be familiar with the style.

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Scatter symbol and the Money symbol. The Wild symbol appears on all the reels while players are in the Free Spins round.
The Scatter symbol appears on all the reels.
When players land 3 or more Scatter symbols, the Free Spin feature is triggered. The greater the number of Scatters, the greater the number of free spins. For example:
While in the Free Spins feature, every Wild symbol gathers value from Fish Money symbols.
Whenever Wilds land during the Free Spins Feature, they are collected and saved to the end of the round. Every fourth Wild gathered retriggers the Free Spins feature and increases the Money symbol multiplier. The feature can be retriggered up to 3 times.
The maximum win is limited to x5000 the player’s total bet, and, if player’s achieve this, the round will end immediately.
The Money symbol is assigned a random value during every spin from x1 to x20. It appears only on the middle reel.
When 3 Money symbols land, this prompts the Hold & Spin Bonus feature. During this feature, the middle reel symbols are held in place and the other reels vanish.
The player begins with 3 respins and any Money symbols that land will reset the respins back to 3. The value of all the middle reel’s Money symbols are added to the player's total win.
The Diamond Money symbol appears on reels 1, 2, 4, and 5 while players are in the Hold & Spin feature. When this symbol lands, it is randomly assigned a value between x100 and x4993.
If player doesn't reach the guaranteed win in the Hold & Spin bonus feature, respins again to 3. Guaranteed win of this feature is player’s total bet x20.

media.caption: Wild symbol collects fish symbol prizes

media.alt: Floating Dragon Hold & Spin respin feature
media.caption: Hold and Spin bonus feature

Bet Sizes, RTP and Variance.text:
The return to player of this game is 96.71%, nicely above our yardstick for average of roughly 96%.
The range of bets on the site we tested ran from a minimum bet per spin of $/£/€0.10 up to a maximum of $/£/€250 per spin.
The volatility of this game is high, which makes it a good match for our preferred slot machine strategies. Our slot strategies target the highest possible volatility.

media.caption: Full paytable for the Floating Dragon Hold and Spin slot

Conclusion.text:
We recommend this high RTP, high volatility Asian kite-themed game.
With excellent mathematical stats and gorgeously animated front end, this game is a great choice for pleasure and maximised wins.
The varied bonus opportunities keep the gameplay engaging and exciting.

title: 777 Strike
overview:
777 Strike
    
        Play 777 Strike demo slot online for fun. Enjoy free casino games in demo mode on Casino Guru. Expert review included.
about_game: This fruit-themed slot has a maximum win ceiling of 2,830x but it is highly volatile.

Theme and Storyline.text:
Red Tiger Gaming has gone for a retro feel with its fruit-themed slot 777 Strike.
Players will notice that Red Tiger Gaming has kept things nice and simple with the layout, as they seek to claim some decent wins.
Those seeking a true classic video slot experience will see that there is nothing elaborate with this title, and there are a couple of neat features.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
From the moment players enter the slot, there is a gameshow vibe to this title. Well, Red Tiger Gaming has tried to give this slot more glitz with its appearance and production values.
The graphics may be basic, and it seems like the backdrop for this slot is on poker felt.
Nevertheless, there has been some thought that has gone into the soundtrack. It is quite upbeat and it packs a punch. Some players may like the light drum beat in the background, to keep them motivated as they progress through the base game.
The visuals may be simplistic and refined, but the quality of the music and sound effects help to carry this game.

Gameplay.text:
Played on a 5x3 reel set, 777 Strike is designed with just 10 fixed paylines in place. There are 9 symbols in place too, and these include a variety of fruits and cards.
Wins can be assembled by landing at least 3 matching symbols across a payline. The cards are the lowest ranked, and the Ace, for example, will offer players a 5.2x return on their wager for a 5-of-a-kind win.
Whereas the lemon is the highest of the fruit symbols, providing a win worth 23x a player’s stake for catching 5 on a payline, while the cherry gives players a win worth 9.2x their stake for 5 cherries.
Wild spins are also part of the package, but we have more details on that later.
The maximum win available for this game is a respectable 2,830x your stake.

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild comes with silver letters and a gold crown on top, and it will substitute for all other regular paying symbols.
To trigger the Free Spins feature, you will need to get 3 free spin symbols on the first, third, and fifth reels to get 7 free spins. Here, there is a chance of a Wild appearing, and the Win Spins will bolster the chance of players getting bigger payouts.
With the Wild Spins, these can come on the last spin of the Win Spins. If players can grab 3 Wild symbols on the first, third, and fifth reels, they will be awarded 7 extra free spins with an extra chance of a Wild appearing.
Each spin will therefore guarantee a win of some form. Wilds will be locked in place throughout the round.
However, it is the 7th Heaven that is a selling point. When free spins mode is retriggered, this can be upgraded for even bigger wins.

Bet Sizes, RTP and Variance.text:
777 Strike carries an RTP of 95.8%, which falls below the industry average of 96%.
The range of bets available on this site ranges from a minimum of $/£/€0.20 per spin, going up to a maximum of $/£/€20 per spin.
Despite that, this game is highly volatile, so players will have to bide their time to claim some big wins.
The high volatility of 777 Strike makes it a great match for our preferred slot machine strategies. We tend to target games that have a good blend of high volatility and RTP.

Conclusion.text:
777 Strike may boast a retro feel, but it more than makes up for that with a great soundtrack and simple, but effective gameplay.
Despite the smaller win potential compared to other fruit-based slots, 777 Strike stands out for the Wild Spins feature, which can see players get some solid returns on their wagers.
The high volatility of this slot means that it will keep players engaged as they make their way through the base game.
However, the disappointingly low RTP is off putting and we wouldn’t be quick to recommend this slot.

about_game: This low RTP (96.05%), high volatility mining-themed slot is not as full of treasure as it should be.

Theme and Storyline.text:
This slot is themed around a fantasy cave filled with gems.
Players will find themselves deep in a shadowy cavern with only torches to guide them. They’ll hunt down precious gems among the damp rocks and with a little luck escape the underground world.
The game has a vaguely steampunk mood with a railroad track running through the mine. Players in the mood for an escape will like the immersive setting.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
An uplifting tune plays in the background, combined with the echoes of water droplets falling. Players will definitely get the sense of being deep in the earth for the duration of the gameplay.
The cave setting is beautifully animated with stoney walls arching around the reels. A bright light suggests the mouth of the cave while flame torches illuminate the interior.
The game’s host is a gremlin-like miner with a half-melted candle atop his head. He smiles mischievously at the start of the game, ensuring that players feel welcome.
The reels are packed with well-cut jewels in tempting colours. Rubies, diamonds and amethysts all sparkle and look ready for the taking.
Overall, the animation and music work well to create a friendly fantasy atmosphere.

media.caption: Base game win in the Cave of Fortune slot machine

Gameplay.text:
Cave of Fortune is a five reel, three row slot, with 30 win lines.
Above each reel sits a counter which accumulates Nitro symbols. Gathering Nitros leads to bonuses (explained below).

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Scatter symbol.
When players collect 3 Nitro symbols in the counter above the reels, they are awarded a Persistent Wild feature. This means that the reel below the counter will transform into a Persistent Wild reel for the following 3 games.
If players achieve a Persistent Wild in all 5 reels at the same time, they will receive a x200 their total bet.
The Scatter symbol may appear on any reel, though only one may appear on each reel. When players land 3 Scatters, they will be awarded 10 free spins. The number of free spins increases to 15 if players land 4 Scatters, and to 20 if players land 5 Scatters.
While in the Free Spins feature, players will be granted a Grand Nitro Meter, which accumulates Nitros. If players accumulate 15 Nitros in this meter, the Grand Jackpot is awarded, meaning x500 the players' total bet.
The Explode feature is triggered at random while players are in the Free Spins feature, providing that the Grand Nitro Meter has reached a count of at least 3. This means that Bomb Wild symbols will be positioned on the reels at random.

Bet Sizes, RTP and Variance.text:
The return to player of this game is 96.04%, roughly our average yardstick for the industry.
The range of bets on the site we tested ran from a minimum bet per spin of $/£/€0.30 up to a maximum of $/£/€60.00 per spin.
The volatility of this game is high, which makes it a good match for our preferred slot machine strategies. Our slot strategies target the highest possible volatility.

media.caption: High paying symbols of the Cave of Fortune slot machine

Conclusion.text: We recommend this medium RTP, high volatility fantasy cave-themed slot.

Theme and Storyline.text:
This slot is themed around the mythical lost city of Atlantis.

Players will snag treasure in the depths of the ocean while enjoying the reef scenery. Those in the mood for a whimsical adventure will especially enjoy this game.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
The soundtrack is a mysterious classical melody that livens up upon spins. Wins are celebrated with an exciting chiming that makes it feel like players are solving the puzzle of the strange world.
The architecture of the city will bring to mind the majestic cities of the ancient Greek world. Little details such as the shells carved above the pillars help reinforce the ocean theme.
Due to the undersea setting, the entire world is tinged blue, with waves gently pulsing above the players and catching sunlight. The animation is self-aware of its cartoon style and is high quality.
The reels are filled with valuable relics such as harps, swords, and vases. A pearl in a clam shell looks tempting and seems right at home in a place adorned with colourful coral.

Gameplay.text:
Atlantean GigaRise is a five reel slot with up to 8 rows, depending on the Trident symbol, which has the power to increase the height of a reel by +1.
Players are awarded wins for landing at least three matching symbols in adjacent reels, from left to right.
The gameplay has a good pace and will keep the players engaged.

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild symbol substitutes for all regular symbols.
The Bonus game is triggered when players land a Trident symbol on a reel that has reached the maximum height.
When the Bonus game begins, players will have the option of three different prize sets. While in the feature, there is one payline, and any symbol that lands in it provides a prize. These prizes include up to x20 players’ bets, free spins, as well as free spins with guaranteed Bonus games.
After the Bonus game concludes, the triggering reel is reduced to a height of 3 rows.
The Free Spins feature is launched when players land 3 or more Free Spin symbols. The number of free spins they receive goes up for landing more Free Spin symbols.

Bonus round has just a single winning line

Gameplay.text:
Perfect Potions Megaways uses the Megaways system, which means that the number of symbols in each reel is randomised in each spin.
Players are awarded wins for landing matching symbols in adjacent rows from left to right.
A cascade feature means that winning symbols will disappear to make way for fresh symbols to take their place.

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Bonus symbol, as well as the Red and Blue Potion symbols. Wild symbols will only appear after the Red potion is activated, and will not appear on the first reel.
Every time a player spins, 1 to 5 Potions will appear randomly above reels 2-6. The Potions will be either Red or Blue.
The Potions will drop to the lowest position available on the reel after winning combinations are removed. If a Potion reaches the bottom of the reels, it will drop into a Caldron and trigger a particular modifier.
If it is the Red Potion that is triggered, all the symbols in the corresponding reels become Wild. If the Blue Potion is triggered, the corresponding reel will expand to double its height.
The Free Spins feature is triggered when players have collected 4 or more Bonus symbols in the Bonus meter. Greater numbers of Bonus symbols will trigger higher numbers of additional spins.

overview:

about_game: This slightly high RTP (96.20%), high volatility vintage cartoon-themed slot is adorably-eerie and filled with fun.

Stack Em review.text:
Stack Em has a vintage cartoon theme with an aesthetic that brings to mind the first pieces animated by Disney.
Players will wander into a wholesome natural scene and meet a pair of springy characters. They bob up and down on either side of a reel of vintage symbols.
This slot is a good fit for players feeling nostalgic for retro cartoons or those who’ve enjoyed getting into Cuphead.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
The whimsical percussion soundtrack upholds the retro mood of the game, and bubble sounds accompany the movement of the reels.
As one might expect in an old-fashioned cartoon, the backdrop behind the reels is much more lushly animated than the characters. Players will see a peaceful landscape of trees and fields that give a relaxed feeling.
Stack Em’s kooky mascot, Canny the Can, is dressed in a pair of white gloves and an elegant tophat, bringing to mind the iconic cartoons of the 1930s. His unmoving grin is almost unsettling, but right on theme for this game.
Canny’s companion, a tiny ink-black mouse named Mona, bounces on the other side of the reels looking adorable and a bit fearful.
The symbols are animated in an engaging vintage style with an eclectic collection of items including leaves, skulls, dead birds, snakes, and hands giving a thumbs up. These cryptic symbols give this game an eerie undertone, despite its cute first impression.
Overall, the soundtrack and animation capture the energy and vibe of vintage cartoons.

Gameplay.text:
Stack Em is a five reel, six row slot.
Players are awarded wins for landing at least 5 connected matching symbols.
When players land a winning combination, the winning symbols remain on the reels and the non-winning symbols fall away, allowing players to build bigger winning combinations.

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
The Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Free Spins symbol.
When players land a win, a multiplier value appears below each reel with a winning symbol. This number reflects the number of winning symbols present in the reel. This collection of multipliers is combined to create a larger multiplier that is applied to players' winnings.
When players land 3 or more Free Spins symbols, the Free Spins feature begins, starting with five free spins.
Throughout the feature, wins increase a multiplier that is applied to players’ winnings.
The Free Spins feature also allows a special X symbol to appear. When the X symbol is pat of a winning combination, the multiplier is applied to the value of the win.
A Question Mark symbol is also added to the reels. When this Question Mark symbol lands it provides a random benefit from a list that includes things like additional free spins and multiplier increases.

Bet Sizes, RTP and Variance.text:
The return to player of this game is 96.20%, slightly above our yardstick for average of roughly 96%.
The range of bets on the site we tested ran from a minimum bet per spin of $/£/€0.20 up to a maximum of $/£/€100 per spin.
Coming in with high volatility, Stack Em is a good match for our preferred slot machine strategies. Our slot strategies target the highest possible volatility.

Conclusion.text:
We recommend this slightly high RTP (96.20%), high volatility vintage cartoon-themed slot.
With respectable RTP and robust volatility, this game is a good choice for mathematically minded players.
The cute yet creepy elements of the theme add extra interest to this engaging slot, as do the variety of bonus features.

about_game: This average RTP (96%), high volatility animal-themed game offers some fantasy safari fun.

Theme and Storyline.text:
This slot has a safari animal theme.
Set on the African savanna, this game is filled with adorable wild animals. Players will meet meerkats, zebras, and leopards. All have welcoming expressions, except for the intimidating alligator.
This game is a good choice for animal lovers, or those looking for a warm exotic escape.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
The soundtrack is filled with drums and wind instruments that add an air of mystery. The steady beat ups the tension and helps create the feel of an adventure. The music speeds up and incorporates vocals as players spin, further increasing the drama.
The animation of the wildlife generally portrays them as friendly and cute. The meerkat seems to smile slightly and the zebra's eyes are large and docile. These stand in contrast to the teeth-baring, red-eyed expression of the alligator.
One notable issue is that though all the other animals are definitely African, as is the iconic savanna setting, alligators are a New World animal. The game creators may have done better to make the game's namesake a 'Croc' or crocodile. This inconsistency doesn't impact gameplay, but savvy animal-lovers will probably notice it.
The beautiful landscape behind the reels will remind players of the Lion King. The scene includes golden savanna, iconic acacias trees, and a peaceful oasis. This natural beauty will help immerse players in their foreign setting.
The reels seem to be crafted from stone, and on either side there are totem poles. This is another point of inconsistency as the totem poles seem to have more in common with Native American cultures than African art. Though this is a minor detail, it suggests the game is leaning on stereotypes of tribal culture rather than portraying a cohesive African world.
Overall, the animation and music have many good points, though observant players may pause at some of the inconsistencies.

media.caption: Base game win in the Gator Gold GigaBlox slot machine

Gameplay.text:
Gator Gold uses a system that randomizes the number of symbols on the reels for every spin.
Wins are awarded for landing at least 3 matching symbols on adjacent reels, starting from left to right.

The Wild symbol substitutes for all regular symbols.
The Gigablox symbols are an extra-large version of a given symbol that pay out as if they are multiple symbols. The game is coded to ensure at least one Gigablox symbol lands on every spin.
The Golden Gator symbol will pay out when only 2 symbols land.
Players will trigger the Free Spins feature when they land 5 or more Free Spin symbols. The number of free spins awarded to the player increases when a greater number of Free Spin symbols land.
During the Free Spins feature, players can land Multiplier Wild symbols which will carry multipliers of x2, and x3. However, these Multiplier Wilds will only be applied to wins that they are part of.

Theme and Storyline.text:
This slot has a safari animal theme.
Players enter a fantasy jungle filled with lush foliage and supernatural animals. Flamingos, zebras, tigers, fish, and frogs all peer out from the reels with glowing eyes. The eerie creatures seem imbued with special powers that they might share.
Players will enjoy communing with nature as they explore the exotic setting.

Graphics, Sounds and Animations.text:
The soundtrack is a holiday-ready tune featuring steel drums. This chill music adds an exotic atmosphere, but definitely seems more cheerful than some of the other aesthetics. The majestically magical animals might have better suited an ominous fantasy track. However, many players will probably enjoy the upbeat vibe of the soundtrack, and if not, mute is readily at hand.
The quality of the animation is decent with its vivid colour palette and consistent style. The jungle setting behind the reels is immersive as green light pours in from above. This suggests that the sunlight is being filtered through a dense roof of leaves. On either side of the reels, dainty flowers are blooming, adding a festive touch.
The highlight of the game are the enchanted animals. The stylised portrayal of each creature, as well as their glowing eyes, suggest that these are no ordinary jungle creatures.
The flamingo in particular has a slightly possessed look, and the design of its face makes it look a little like a dinosaur. One might expect it to speak cryptically in a rasping voice.
The showstopper is the hippo, who seems almost like a deity cast in gold. The hippo stares out directly at the players with an expression that is both sombre and intimidating.
Overall, the animation and music create a fun fantasy jungle world, though it’s a little unclear whether the magic is whimsical or ominous.

media.caption: Base game win in the Hippo Pop slot machine

Gameplay.text:
Hippo Pop has a five reel, three row base structure. However, after a winning combination, the winning symbols are replaced by 2 symbols increasing the size of the reels up to six symbols high during regular gameplay and eight symbols high during the Free Spins feature.
This game awards payouts whenever players land at least 3 matching symbols in adjacent rows, starting from left to right.
Players have the option to buy directly into the Free Spins feature if they wish (see feature details below).

media.caption: Gameplay video

Wilds, Bonuses and Free Spins.text:
Should players fully expand the reels during the base game, a multiplier count up begins and will continue until there are no more wins. After the base game wins are paid out, the Free Spins feature is triggered.
The Free Spins feature begins with the reels standing 3 symbols high, but will allow them to increase to 8 symbols high given enough wins.
The Free Spins also begin with a multiplier that is carried over from the base game.
The Free Spins Hippo Payout feature means that Hippo symbols will pay out more when the reels are higher. When the reels reach 6 symbols high, the Hippo symbol will pay out x2 its base value. The Hippo symbol will then payout x3 its base value if the reels reach 7 symbols high, and x4 its value should the reels reach the maximum of 8 symbols high.
Players will receive 2 additional free spins should they unlock the maximum height of the reels.
Players are offered 5 free spins of the Bonus Wheel as they begin the Free Spins feature. This provides the chance at extra prizes.
